node.title: NZ Cricket confirm radio commentary deal with SENZ
node.description: Live, ball-by-ball commentary of all home cricket internationals and domestic finals will be available on SENZ radio this summer.
node.content:
["", "
\nPhoto: 123RF\n
", "Live, ball-by-ball commentary of all home cricket internationals and domestic finals will be available on SENZ radio this summer.", "Digital coverage also accessible via a partnership with NZME and the Alternative Commentary Collective.", "New Zealand Cricket has signed a new four-year partnership with SENZ to provide comprehensive coverage of all Black Caps and White Ferns home internationals, as well as all finals from the domestic men's and women's Super Smash and one-day competitions.", "SEN in Australia will take the feed for this summer's home Tests against Australia, and in turn SENZ will carry coverage of the White Ferns three T20 internationaIs in Australia, to be played in October 2025.", "NZC will announce its 2023-24 home international schedule this week.", "-RNZ"]
